-- Louise Toolkit seed: home page sections ONLY (no site_settings).
-- Use this to populate/refresh the marketing landing content without touching
-- the site_settings singleton (nav/social links, etc.) — safe on a production DB
-- whose Settings have been customized. For a full first-time seed (home +
-- settings) use home-and-settings.seed.sql instead.
--
-- Apply to the remote pre-prod DB:
--   cd workers/site && npx wrangler d1 execute DB --remote --file=seed/home.seed.sql
-- Local dev (miniflare):
--   cd workers/site && npx wrangler d1 execute DB --local --file=seed/home.seed.sql
-- Idempotent (INSERT OR REPLACE by id); no BEGIN/COMMIT (D1 forbids SQL txns on --remote).
